  '<h3 id="http-client-interceptors">b.httpClient.request({ before, after }) <a class="anchor" href="#http-client-interceptors">#</a></h3>',
  '<p><code>before</code> hooks mutate or replace the request opts; <code>after</code> hooks observe the final opts + response. Operators inject auth headers, observability, audit emits without wrapping <code>request</code>. <code>before</code> throws surface as <code>BEFORE_THREW</code>. <code>after</code> throws are caught — a broken hook never blocks the response.</p>',
  '<pre><code class="language-javascript">var reqShape = {',
