  '<p>SafeUrl gates protocol + userinfo, ssrfGuard gates IP class — the third layer is the destination hostname. Operators with strict egress policies pin the upstreams the app is allowed to talk to so a compromised process can\'t reach arbitrary destinations. A request to a host outside the allowlist throws with code <code>HOST_DISALLOWED</code> before the socket opens.</p>',
  '<pre><code class="language-javascript">var reqShape = {',
